    "What are the performance gaps in the industry?": "Many organizations struggle with efficiently scaling their IT infrastructure to meet fluctuating demands. There's often a lack of understanding on how to choose the right cloud services, leading to overspending or underperformance. Legacy systems can be difficult to integrate, causing delays and compatibility issues, ultimately impacting agility and innovation.",
